altText: Two gloved hands hold a gray rock of uranium ore.

article_heading: U.S. Ramps Up Hunt for Uranium to End Reliance on Russia
altText: A tall structure sits atop ground with an ominous sky beyond.

article_heading: U.S. Ramps Up Hunt for Uranium to End Reliance on Russia
altText: Mable Franklin, wearing a blue T-shirt and a pink and maroon patterned skirt, stands on dark earth, her gray hair blowing in the wind.

article_heading: U.S. Ramps Up Hunt for Uranium to End Reliance on Russia
altText: A plywood billboard in an expansive field of grass and sagebrush says: “Radioactive pollution kills. It’s time to clean up the mines.”

article_heading: U.S. Ramps Up Hunt for Uranium to End Reliance on Russia
altText: Carletta Tilousi, wearing a light blue top with beaded embroidery and a matching light blue skirt with a row of multicolor ribbons, stands in a golden field. One of her hands, with a large turquoise bracelet, is on her forehead while the other is resting on a black leather belt with silver buckles.

article_heading: U.S. Ramps Up Hunt for Uranium to End Reliance on Russia
altText: Three rows of green and gray barrels are stacked on sandy earth.

article_heading: U.S. Ramps Up Hunt for Uranium to End Reliance on Russia
altText: Mounds of dark brown earth on a sandy surface underneath blue sky and clouds.

article_heading: U.S. Ramps Up Hunt for Uranium to End Reliance on Russia
altText: John W. Cash, wearing a white hard hat, safety glasses, a white button-down shirt, bluejeans and work boots, kneels beside a pump in a sandy field with patches of grass.

article_heading: U.S. Ramps Up Hunt for Uranium to End Reliance on Russia
altText: Mark Chalmers, wearing a blue hard hat and glasses, stands in front of an industrial structure.

article_heading: U.S. Ramps Up Hunt for Uranium to End Reliance on Russia
altText: Five glass vials sit in a wooden holder on top of a wood table. The samples vary in color, from clear to green to yellow, and viscosity.

article_heading: U.S. Ramps Up Hunt for Uranium to End Reliance on Russia
altText: Blue and gray machines with multiple blue dials in an industrial mill.

article_heading: U.S. Ramps Up Hunt for Uranium to End Reliance on Russia
altText: A white building with windows missing panes on a dry yellow field. Old gas pumps sit on one side of the building.

article_heading: U.S. Ramps Up Hunt for Uranium to End Reliance on Russia
altText: A gray car with its back wheels missing sits in front of a chain-link fence, with other crates and rubbish. Behind is a house on the right and a trailer on the left.
